title: Larry Norman - Totally Unplugged - (a)live and kicking (192k)
description:
One of Larry's better acoustic live albums from 1994.  Most of the songs are from the "Stranded in Babylon" album.  

Tracklist

1. Introduction/Watch What You're Doing
2. Texas and Me
3. Step Into the Madness
4. Why Should The Devil
5. Weight of the World
6. Baby's Got The Blues
7. I Hope I'll See You In Heaven
8. A Woman of God
9. Let The Rain Fall Down On Me
10. All The Way Home
11. I Will Survive

This album is pretty hard to find.  Sharing is caring!  Ripped at 192k mp3
